            <div type="transcript" id="F8A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>When Roses cease to bloom, Sir,</l>
                    <l>And Violets are done - </l>
                    <l>When Bumblebees in solemn flight </l>
                    <l>Have passed beyond the Sun - </l>
                    <l>The hand that paused to gather</l>
                    <l>Opon this Summer's day </l>
                    <l>Will idle lie - in Auburn - </l>
                    <l>Then take my flowers - pray!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
